name: #02 TABASKI, Mamadou Sow x Papa Sow 2021, 2/2
description: What looks like an colorful fabric from Africa is the product of a digital manipulation I made from an original oil painting that my father made 1997. The colors and shapes express the vibrant energy that you experience during the Tabaski fest in Senegal. Tabaski is a holiday where the family comes together, eats, dances and the children receive presents. This NFT represents the value of Family and Culture.
